      <title>伊朗革命卫队在霍尔木兹海峡附近扣押集装箱船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-13/urgent-british-military-warns-of-possible-vessel-being-boarded-near-strait-of-hormuz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国迪拜（美联社）——周六，伊朗准军事革命卫队的突击队员从直升机上用绳索降落到霍尔木兹海峡附近的一艘以色列附属集装箱船上，并扣押了该船，这是两国之间的最新袭击事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-13/urgent-british-military-warns-of-possible-vessel-being-boarded-near-strait-of-hormuz</guid>
